Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:26.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}背中押してる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:29.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}「さあ、行こう、ほら」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.69,0:22:32.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}大切なもの　探すのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.82,0:22:35.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}見たことないあの場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.74,0:22:40.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}ステキに会える予感だけ持ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.69,0:22:43.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}それで十分でしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.14,0:22:46.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}広がるファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.62,0:22:52.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}今を超えて　その旅路へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:22:55.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}止まれない　すぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:56.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}Follow Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:22:59.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}愛・愛・愛を引き連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:02.10,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}素直なBRAVE　踏み出せば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.30,0:23:07.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}描ききれない  地図のカケラ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.54,0:23:08.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}絶対！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:11.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}愛　会いたいと思うなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:13.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}強気なBREATH　吸い込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:18.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}夢の続きにまた夢を見よう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:29.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}あなたと　叶えたい　明日へ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,//--------------------OPCN--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:24.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}桃色微风将我包裹起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:26.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}推动我前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:29.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}「来吧  出发  赶紧」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.69,0:22:32.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}寻找重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.82,0:22:35.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}就要向着未曾见过的那片地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.74,0:22:40.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}如果预感能与你完美邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.69,0:22:43.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}那样就足够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.14,0:22:46.62,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}延伸的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.62,0:22:52.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}跨越现在  踏上那段旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:22:55.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}已经  无法停止脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:56.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}Follow Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:22:59.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}爱·爱·爱  带上我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:02.10,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}率直的BRAVE  只要迈出这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.30,0:23:07.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}无法绘制完毕  地图的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.54,0:23:08.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}绝对！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:11.03,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}只要念着遇见爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:13.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}深吸一口积极的BREATH
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:18.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(150,150)}在梦的续篇继续邂逅美梦吧
